# Auto-resolve PROGRESS.md merge conflicts by taking the union of both
# sides' lines. Multiple agents append to PROGRESS.md in parallel and
# it's an append-only ledger — concatenation is the right semantic.
#
# Tradeoff: the "newest on top" ordering can get scrambled if two
# branches both added entries at the head. Manual re-sort after merge
# is fine; nothing is ever lost.
PROGRESS.md merge=union
